com.worizon.jsonrpc.gson

Annotation Type NonExpose


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Target(value=FIELD)
public @interface NonExpose
    This annotation marks a field to be excluded of marshalling when the library converts the object into a JSON String.
    Since:
    1.0.0
